# DroidLens is a cross-platform ADB toolkit (macOS / Linux / Windows Git Bash).
# Shell and Python sources MUST use LF on every platform: CRLF breaks bash shebangs
# (`#!/usr/bin/env bash\r` → "bash\r: not found") and taints parsing in Git Bash, and
# would also break on macOS/Linux. Enforce LF regardless of core.autocrlf.
*.sh  text eol=lf
*.py  text eol=lf
*.bash text eol=lf
